@startuml State Chart - Prediksi Risiko DBD
title State Chart Diagram - Prediksi Risiko DBD\nSistem Prediksi Penyebaran Penyakit Menular DBD

skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor<<blue>> #dae8fc
  BorderColor<<blue>> #6c8ebf
  BackgroundColor<<yellow>> #fff2cc
  BorderColor<<yellow>> #d6b656
  BackgroundColor<<green>> #d5e8d4
  BorderColor<<green>> #82b366
  BackgroundColor<<red>> #f8cecc
  BorderColor<<red>> #b85450
  BackgroundColor<<purple>> #e1d5e7
  BorderColor<<purple>> #9673a6
}

[*] --> FormPrediksi

state "Form Input Prediksi" as FormPrediksi <<blue>> {
}
FormPrediksi : entry / render form prediksi
FormPrediksi : do / input Bulan, Jumlah Kasus,
FormPrediksi :       Usia, Jenis Kelamin,
FormPrediksi :       Lama Rawat Inap

state "Validasi Input Data" as ValidasiInput <<yellow>> {
}
ValidasiInput : entry / cek field required terisi
ValidasiInput : do / validasi tipe data & range nilai

state "Error: Input Tidak Valid" as ErrorInput <<red>> {
}
ErrorInput : entry / tampilkan pesan error

state "Load Model Random Forest" as LoadModel <<yellow>> {
}
LoadModel : entry / load model dari file .pkl
LoadModel : do / cek apakah model tersedia

state "Prediksi Rule-Based (Fallback)" as RuleBased <<yellow>> {
}
RuleBased : entry / model belum tersedia
RuleBased : do / get_risk_level(jumlah_kasus)
RuleBased :       ≤8=Rendah, 9-15=Sedang, >15=Tinggi

state "Prediksi dengan Model RF" as ModelRF <<purple>> {
}
ModelRF : entry / encode fitur input
ModelRF : do / model.predict([usia, rawat, jk])
ModelRF :       predict_proba() → confidence
ModelRF : exit / decode label → tingkat risiko

state "Simpan & Tampilkan Hasil Prediksi" as HasilPrediksi <<green>> {
}
HasilPrediksi : entry / INSERT INTO hasil_prediksi
HasilPrediksi : do / tampilkan tingkat risiko,
HasilPrediksi :       confidence, probabilitas,
HasilPrediksi :       rekomendasi tindakan

FormPrediksi --> ValidasiInput : klik tombol Prediksi
ValidasiInput --> ErrorInput : [input tidak valid]
ErrorInput --> FormPrediksi : perbaiki input
ValidasiInput --> LoadModel : [input valid]
LoadModel --> RuleBased : [model belum ada]
LoadModel --> ModelRF : [model tersedia]
RuleBased --> HasilPrediksi
ModelRF --> HasilPrediksi
HasilPrediksi --> FormPrediksi : prediksi ulang
HasilPrediksi --> [*] : selesai

note right of ModelRF
  Aktor: Pengguna (Petugas / Admin)
  Model: Random Forest → predict & predict_proba
  Fallback: Rule-based jika model belum di-training
  Threshold: ≤8=Rendah, 9-15=Sedang, >15=Tinggi
end note

@enduml
